@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gajpsg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.cos(v2 + 0.26) * (v0 + 0.05 - v2 + 0.03)))
    tmp = (0.73 * wp.abs(0.31))
    v0 = v2
    v2 = ((1.00 - (v1 + 0.42 / tmp + 0.40)) * ((tmp + 0.16 - v2 + 0.29) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.73)))
    v0 = wp.abs(0.36)
    data[tid] = v0
